## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [agg1-1c; agg2-1; agg3-3]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Three to four day-old agg1-1c; agg2-1; agg3-3 seedlings are relatively more tolerant to NAE 18:3 treatment than wild-type (Col-0). Chlorophyll content was reduced statistically significantly more in Col-0 relative to agg1-1c; agg2-1; agg3-3. However, agg1-1c; agg2-1; agg3-3 seedling growth was still reduced by NAE 18:3 treatment.
